longBusinessSummary: Dlala Brokerage and Investment Holding Company Q.P.S.C., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the brokerage activities at the Qatar Exchange. It operates through four segments: Stock Brokerage, Real Estate, Information Technology, and others segments. The company also provides property management, marketing, and sales services for real estate clients; and information technology management and consultation services. In addition, it engages in developing and programming of IT programs; and investment activities. Dlala Brokerage and Investment Holding Company Q.P.S.C. was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Doha, Qatar.
